{"tid":125272,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)五福星系列","createTime":"2017-02-18T10:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T18:45:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95bae582bef4d54a357856957d16474ade7e6dab","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1d1a6f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8b2522db\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7d/Lucky_Stars.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7d%2FLucky_Stars.jpg&h=6682ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/42/Return_of_the_Lucky_Stars_movie_poster_1989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F42%2FReturn_of_the_Lucky_Stars_movie_poster_1989.jpg&h=c0bfcb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://r2.ykimg.com/050E00005302BFCF67583926D60898F0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fr2.ykimg.com%2F050E00005302BFCF67583926D60898F0&h=03d26712&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://image11.m1905.cn/uploadfile/2013/0305/thumb_1_266_360_20130305041059196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage11.m1905.cn%2Fuploadfile%2F2013%2F0305%2Fthumb_1_266_360_20130305041059196.jpg&h=0c06efd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏日福星:鷓鴣菜(洪金寶飾)、羅漢果(曾志偉飾)、花旗蔘(秦祥林飾)、大生地(吳耀漢飾)及犀牛皮(馮淬帆飾)在東京屢破奇案，香港警察特地請他們到泰國芭提雅渡假，而花旗蔘(秦祥林飾)因準備行船，故推薦其弟花塔餅(苗僑偉飾)代替自己加入五福星行列。霸王花(胡慧中飾)同時亦接獲密令，往泰國找線人老馬(黃錦燊飾)，拿一份泰、港毒販名單，但殺手已搶先將其滅口，幸馬於臨終前已將名單寄往香港的王綺清小姐(關芝琳飾)，於是五福星聯同香港警探雞骨草(成龍飾)與獨腳金(元彪飾)會師再戰.....<br />\n<br />\n《福星闖江湖》（英文：Return of the Lucky Stars）是福星系列之一，犀牛皮（馮粹帆）、大山地（吳耀漢）、羅漢果（曾志偉）、花塔餅（苗僑偉）為了幫大哥大（盧海鵬）對付沒有義氣的巫義氣（王青），四位福星勇闖江湖<br />\n<br />\n五福星撞鬼:外號叫&ldquo;鷓鴣菜&rdquo;&ldquo;羅漢果&rdquo;&ldquo;犀牛皮&rdquo;&ldquo;花旗參&rdquo;和&ldquo;大山地&rdquo;的五個香港青年整日想入非非，即想輕鬆賺錢，又想有漂亮的女友相伴，但又不想塌實乾事，結果一事無成，只能得過且過，混日子，打發時光。一次，他們五人一同去旅遊勝地&mdash;&mdash;離島遊玩，卻不料晚上在島上的一棟黑漆漆的大屋內撞到一男一女兩個鬼魂。第二天，他們向有關警局報了警.....<br />\n<br />\n運財五福星:賭王雷天，在一次頂級國際頂級睹術大賽中被賭花上宮飛花陷害而落敗，身敗名裂以至吞槍自殺。其女慧琳誓要為父報仇並求助雷天生前好友華叔，華叔於是重召五福星幫忙&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd9f6a4dcf0891bd9023feed34951df8485c4ed","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f80832991d7eb93e82f24163d9c36f6c87c3fa","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb66c86dd10a96a17507b34dc96ae01b41fe326","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2307604e7568ec3c8e1109617a4a4da97bb037","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd46d85e51f7916364bd6bd7a1da59d06823d7d3","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bba46cbfa3e4a63af20856e109c2017a0fa5ed","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0565f0dccffb664f8e93b16fd45588fa1ece920","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acb0ecbb99b3114ef8c50680025d66a6704e829","tid":125272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}